comments.body:
Thank you @johnnykang for checking. And you are right, that should be the problem. 

The version of [gvproxy has been updated](https://github.com/containers/podman/pull/24394) in 5.3 but [the scoop installer](https://github.com/ScoopInstaller/Main/blob/master/bucket/podman.json) extracts podman.exe, not gvproxy from the installer. 

@baude any idea who maintains the podman scoop bucket? From git history it looks @niheaven is the last one that have updated it.
